{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"237033-kaaso-aru-hohapahu","title":"কাছ আৰু শহাপহু","description":"কাছ আৰু শহাৰ মাজত দৌৰ আৰম্ভ হ'ল।বাটত শহা শুই গ'ল আৰু কাছ আগুৱাই গ'ল। এনেতে কাছই সিংহক লগ পালে। আগলৈ কি হ'ব বাৰু?","language":"Assamese","langCode":"as","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Pinku Moni Nath"],"illustrators":["Padmanabh"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Education Foundation","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/237033-kaaso-aru-hohapahu"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/282978/size3/f0f4bc971ee80853a0691be353e006a1.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/282978/size6/f0f4bc971ee80853a0691be353e006a1.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/276884/size6/8a972a18784425a4eee31eeb0f452fac.jpg","text":"2/11","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/276886/size6/ca2786bf40af15f701e5bcdba8fdebbe.jpg","text":"এখন অৰণ্যত আছিল দুজন বন্ধু।\nএটা কাছ আৰু আনটো শহাপহু।","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/276889/size6/4e9a0a5bc4587b2f0c71b3d84900f0c8.jpg","text":"বন্ধুত্ব আছিল দুয়োৰে নলেগলে লগা।\nকৰে একেলগে দুয়ো খেলা-খোৱা।","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/276907/size6/6c4f63c80f4804c94ce43ee1cad779d4.jpg","text":"শহাৰ মনত আহিল এটা কথা।\nএদিন সি ক'লে কাছক সেই কথা।","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/276908/size6/9808e442d9b1da011e869b57196a4a78.jpg","text":"কাছই কথাত হয়ভৰ দিলে।\nতাৰ পাছত দুয়ো দৌৰ দিলে।","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/276910/size6/cdd36e190177873b73679a159b6a4b25.jpg","text":"দৌৰি দৌৰি শহা শুই গ'ল।\nকাছই পিছে আগুৱাই গ'ল।","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/276913/size6/9f51ac4376bbac1d7744564be2e2af89.jpg","text":"সিংহ এটাক বাটত পালে লগ।\nভয়তে কাছৰ লাগিল জটপট।","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/276915/size6/d619f12378f070c2df7becc3e134855b.jpg","text":"তেনেতে শহাই সাৰ পালে।\nবন্ধুক বিচাৰি বেগাই লৰ দিলে।","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/276916/size6/2d4ef3eb3f7aba4958481dd2d13362f6.jpg","text":"সিংহক দেখি কথাটো বুজি পালে।\nদুয়োৰে মাজত শহাই জাপ দিলে।","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/276919/size6/de7e1d283c2fc4b1608fbedb2b993eea.jpg","text":"কাছ উঠিল জাপ মাৰি শহাৰ পিঠিত।\nশহা দৌৰি বচালে জীৱন দুয়োৰে।","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":10,"words":88}}